Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是FRAU KOUJIRO吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊 笔名什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说古郡是真名？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 古郡可奈 从明天开始转进咱们高中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可奈…
